---
import GlobalLayout from "../layouts/GlobalLayout.astro";
import AdvisoryRule from "../components/AdvisoryRule.astro";
import site from "../config.json";
---

<GlobalLayout title="About" description={`Mission, story, and credentials of ${site.principal} — ${site.brand}.`}>
  <section class="relative bg-ink text-ivory overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grain opacity-20 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-dark-radial opacity-60 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gold/25 shadow-goldring">
        <img
          src="/images/gda/Professional%20financial%20seminar%20in%20session.png"
          alt="Professional financial education seminar in session"
          width="900"
          height="1200"
          class="w-full h-auto object-cover object-[center_25%]"
          loading="eager"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <AdvisoryRule label="Our story" class="justify-start mb-6" />
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight">About {site.principal}</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-ivory/78 font-sans text-lg leading-relaxed">
          {site.brand} exists to move people from uncertainty to clarity—and from survival to legacy—through education,
          mentorship, and purpose-aligned strategy.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-ivory/70 font-sans text-base leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
          You are not handed off to a script. The work begins with listening—then helping you see your options in plain
          language, at a pace that honors your faith and your family.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-ivory/55 font-sans border-l-2 border-gold/50 pl-4">
          {site.affiliation}. Educational context only; not a solicitation where not permitted.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-ivory border-t border-ink/5">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 space-y-8 font-sans text-lg text-body/90 leading-relaxed">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-ink">Mission &amp; vision</h2>
      <p>
        {site.brand} was created to help people make confident financial decisions with education, faith, and practical
        strategy working together. The work begins with clarity: where you are, what you want to protect, and what kind
        of legacy you are building.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every conversation is designed to be <strong class="text-ink">hope-forward and precise</strong>—focused on
        understanding, protection, leadership, and next steps that fit your real life.
      </p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-card border-l-4 border-l-gold">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Education first</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Principles you can repeat at the kitchen table—before products ever enter the chat.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-card border-l-4 border-l-gold">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Strategic protection</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Guarding the engine—your income and priorities—so optimism has a backbone.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-card border-l-4 border-l-gold">
          <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Long-horizon legacy</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Plans that flex when life does—without losing sight of generational stewardship.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-sand/40 p-8">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">From concern to clarity (how a session often flows)</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-muted">
          Illustrative only—your story is unique. This is the shape many education-first conversations take.
        </p>
        <ol class="mt-6 space-y-6 list-none p-0">
          <li class="relative pl-10">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink text-gold text-sm font-bold font-sans" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
            <p class="font-semibold text-ink">The concern</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-base text-muted">
              Busy schedules, mixed messages online, and the quiet fear that “we should be further along by now.”
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="relative pl-10">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink text-gold text-sm font-bold font-sans" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
            <p class="font-semibold text-ink">The discovery</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-base text-muted">
              A simple map of cash flow, protection, and positioning—so trade-offs make sense in human terms, not headlines.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="relative pl-10">
            <span class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink text-gold text-sm font-bold font-sans" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
            <p class="font-semibold text-ink">The next faithful step</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-base text-muted">
              One or two priorities for the next 30–90 days—plus an invitation to return when you are ready for depth.
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink/10 bg-sand/50 p-8">
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Credentials snapshot</h3>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gold">◆</span> Licensed financial professional, WFG</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gold">◆</span> Education-first sessions and structured mentorship</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-gold">◆</span> Focus on protection, clarity, and long-term legacy</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="/book" class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-gold-shine px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-bold text-ink shadow-lift hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
          Book a conversation
        </a>
        <a href="/programs" class="inline-flex rounded-full border border-ink/15 px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-ink hover:bg-sand transition-colors">
          View programs
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14 bg-charcoal border-t border-gold/15">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold/80 font-sans mb-4">Glorious Destiny Advisory</p>
      <img
        src="/images/gda/logo-horizontal-dark.png"
        alt="Glorious Destiny Advisory"
        width="1400"
        height="420"
        class="w-full border border-gold/20 shadow-lift bg-ivory"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</GlobalLayout>
